# Agent Architecture
# AI 智能体系统架构

This document explains the architecture of the Emotion-Aware AI Agent.

（本文档说明 CBT-AI-Emotional-Support-Agent 的系统架构）

---

## Core Architecture

The system consists of several functional modules.

系统由多个功能模块组成：

1 User Input Layer  
用户输入层

Receives user messages and sends them to the analysis module.

接收用户输入。

---



---

2 Memory Storage & Retrieval  
长期记忆系统

Stores important conversation information and retrieves relevant memories.

保存对话关键内容并提供检索能力。

---

3 Conversation Stage Classification + Emotion Detection & State Analysis  
情绪识别与亲密度（关系）状态分析

The system analyzes:

系统分析：

• Emotional tone  
• Conversation context  
• User intent
对话阶段判断

The system determines the current conversation stage:

系统判断当前阶段：

• Engagement  
• Exploration  
• Intervention  
• Closure

---

4 不同阶段模型+ Prompt Strategy Module  
Prompt 策略模块

Selects different prompt templates based on conversation stage.

根据分流进入的不同阶段模型 对应不同 Prompt 模板。

---

5 Response Generation  
回复生成

The language model generates responses according to the selected strategy.

语言模型根据策略生成回复。

---

6 Response Review Model  
AI 回复评估模型

The system evaluates the generated response before storing it in memory.

系统会对生成的回复进行评估。

Evaluation dimensions include:

评估维度包括：

• Emotional empathy  
• Conversation coherence  
• Psychological support quality  
• Safety compliance

Evaluation results are stored in the memory system.

评估结果会存入长期记忆系统。

---

7 Output Processing  
输出处理

The system processes responses using sentence segmentation and pause handling.

系统对回复进行断句与停顿处理，使对话更自然。

